    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1221250/extras/6c0dbd5b6a2e5891f36540eca537d9b7.avif?t=1766090728\" width=500 height=281 /></span><br><br>《诺科》作为一款指向点击叙事冒险游戏，美国南部哥特色彩浓郁，引领玩家走进路易斯安那州扭曲的南部，走进行将沉没的城郊与绿意盎然的工业沼泽。妈妈去世了，弟弟布雷克也因此失踪了，你想找到他，只好跟着一个鬼鬼祟祟的安保赛博格穿过新奥尔良城郊的一座又一座炼油厂、露天商场和废水沟。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>全心浸入路易斯安那州离奇而又古怪的南部</strong></h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1221250/extras/4ed43838abbcb323d5f51ca95b8cd499.webp?t=1766090728\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1221250/extras/4ed43838abbcb323d5f51ca95b8cd499.poster.avif?t=1766090728\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=347 /></picture></span><br>《诺科》的场景灵感源自路易斯安那周州同名城市诺科和大新奥尔良地区的其他地点，像素美术笔触清晰，电影质感鲜明，引领玩家细细品味科幻世界，走进即将消失的沼地，步入迷宫一般的石油加工厂，邂逅其他形形色色的地方。醉心于fmAura丰富的实地录音和声音设计，感受Gewgawly I有力的后工业风电子音乐。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>过去迟迟不去，未来的乌云却已出现，秘密等你来揭晓。</strong></h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1221250/extras/7637af164dc72ef05bcfe4012d1d78ff.poster.avif?t=1766090728\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1221250/extras/7637af164dc72ef05bcfe4012d1d78ff.webm?t=1766090728\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1221250/extras/7637af164dc72ef05bcfe4012d1d78ff.mp4?t=1766090728\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>简简单单的寻弟之旅迅速卷入了一个牵涉几代人的谜团。拯救、往事、科技与自然的界线融在一起，植根于美国南部文学、地摊文学和新旧派指向点击冒险游戏。汇成一段独具特色、引人入胜、发人深思的叙事。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏角色背景复杂，故事丰富，行事动机令人玩味。</strong></h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1221250/extras/d5a590ea110f157458398836986eafd0.webp?t=1766090728\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1221250/extras/d5a590ea110f157458398836986eafd0.poster.avif?t=1766090728\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=347 /></picture></span><br>世界渐渐销蚀，事事都不确定，不过糊里糊涂的河匪、嗜酒如命的私家侦探、脱逃的安保仿生人和你儿时的毛绒猴子都会助你一臂之力。破解道道谜题，突破重重难关，搞定集团的安保打手，潜入某个网红组织在新奥尔良城郊盘踞的某个荒废商场。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1221250/extras/529610a5d88e0d6613854f33302fca8b.poster.avif?t=1766090728\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1221250/extras/529610a5d88e0d6613854f33302fca8b.webm?t=1766090728\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1221250/extras/529610a5d88e0d6613854f33302fca8b.mp4?t=1766090728\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
